{
  "texts": [
    "Defenses based on detection are focused on determining the integrity of a given data prompt [104], [225], [241], [269].",
    "Notably, the proactive detection method [225] has proven effective in identifying instances of prompt injection attacks.",
    "Defenses based on detection can further be classified into two categories: response-based detection, and prompt-based detection.",
    "A response-based detection method examines the response of LLMs, while a prompt-based detection approach examines a provided data prompt.",
    "Perplexity-based detection is a kind of prompt-based detection."
  ]
}